  "siteName": "机器之心SOTA模型",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">🏆基座模型</span></strong></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">①项目：T5Gemma 2</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-height=\"406\" data-imgfileid=\"100017312\" data-ratio=\"0.3490740740740741\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1162\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=cb4f7a53&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkzQ4Kn3JjytVz56B2rJYNRRt9Ro7UibLajXjjK5Zaib1XY7NLcibASH0yteMqiazAheHXQSsgvxibcoBUQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★T5Gemma 2是Google开发的一系列轻量级但功能强大的编码器-解码器研究模型。该模型通过将预训练的仅解码器Gemma模型改编为编码器-解码器模型而构建。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">T5Gemma 2基于</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">Gemma 3</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">，支持</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">多语言</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">和</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">多模态</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">，能够处理文本和图像输入并生成文本输出。该模型具有开放权重，适用于多种文本生成和图像理解任务，如问答、摘要和推理。其相对较小的规模使其可以在资源有限的环境中部署，如笔记本电脑、台式机或个人云基础设施。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/t5gemma-2\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/t5gemma-2</a></span></span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">②项目：FunctionGemma</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-height=\"332\" data-imgfileid=\"100017310\" data-ratio=\"0.2861111111111111\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1162\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=2df43fa6&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkzQ4Kn3JjytVz56B2rJYNRRY72tAmOyjmH0caANdDVzvDkrbibdW4j5ibnQPRBB9jtucnyzMxSd0RMA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★FunctionGemma是谷歌推出的一个轻量级开放模型，专为函数调用任务而设计。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">该模型基于</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">Gemma 3-270M</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">模型构建，适合在</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">资源有限</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">的环境中部署，如笔记本电脑、台式机或云基础设施。FunctionGemma经过优化，能够在多种硬件上高效运行，尤其适合单轮或多轮任务的特定数据微调。该模型的应用案例包括语音控制的互动游戏和移动设备的操作Agent，展示了其在特定领域的高性能表现。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p><span style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/functiongemma\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/functiongemma</a></span></span></span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">③项目：3DGen-R1</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5453703703703704\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1162\" data-height=\"634\" data-imgfileid=\"100017313\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f55b5f26&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkzQ4Kn3JjytVz56B2rJYNRRfiavMUVlLMAH6r1dGxhvOL2ocyaDGMbT0ZGLZqFt7J2SwkyWyLM9LOw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">★</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">3DGen-R1是一个用于文本到3D生成的项目，旨在探索强化学习在该领域的应用潜力。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">该项目提供了官方实现，并伴随相关的研究论文，探讨了在文本到3D生成中应用强化学习的准备情况。项目提供了一步生成模型的检查点和推理代码，用户可以通过安装相关环境和依赖来进行推理。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p><span style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/3dgen-r1\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/3dgen-r1</a></span></span></span></p>\n  <p><strong><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;strong&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:null},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">④</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">项目：SoFlow</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-height=\"426\" data-imgfileid=\"100017316\" data-ratio=\"0.36666666666666664\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1162\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=5a9fc86a&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkzQ4Kn3JjytVz56B2rJYNRRUia0HYPJZEZonEFqI8aHMVJKh6M3kQPY4kMwF6KialOOFy8bYL8qUSibw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★SoFlow是一个用于单步生成建模的解决方案流模型。该项目由普林斯顿大学的研究人员开发，旨在通过结合变分自编码器（VAE）和扩散模型的优势，实现高效的图像生成。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">SoFlow的实现基于</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">PyTorch</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">，支持ImageNet和CIFAR-10数据集的生成任务。项目提供了详细的代码结构和训练流程，便于用户快速上手。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p><span style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/soflow\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/soflow</a></span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">🛠️ 框架平台、必备工具</span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">①项目：MNN</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-height=\"420\" data-imgfileid=\"100017315\" data-ratio=\"0.3611111111111111\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1162\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f997ba19&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkzQ4Kn3JjytVz56B2rJYNRRS6eN7yZsVdJMNQVzxMCT8wxSFrZQ33ZlOLo0ncDiboKHk2Q1I412wyA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★MNN是一个高效且轻量级的深度学习框架，支持深度学习模型的推理和训练，具有行业领先的设备端推理和训练性能。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">目前，MNN已集成到阿里巴巴的30多个应用中，覆盖70多种使用场景，如直播、短视频捕捉、搜索推荐、以图搜物、互动营销等。此外，MNN还用于物联网等嵌入式设备。MNN-LLM是基于MNN引擎开发的大语言模型运行时解决方案，支持在移动设备、PC和物联网平台上本地部署流行的大语言模型。MNN-Diffusion是基于MNN引擎开发的稳定扩散模型运行时解决方案，旨在本地部署稳定扩散模型。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/mnn-alibaba\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/mnn-alibaba</a></span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"3 3 []\"><strong><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;strong&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:null},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">②</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">项目：ContextGen</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-height=\"804\" data-imgfileid=\"100017314\" data-ratio=\"0.6907407407407408\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1164\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=4a400730&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkzQ4Kn3JjytVz56B2rJYNRRKP6ZkaRa4CJxwnUUd1R8672GPDic7Tk4UJR0SJXxW7OEZDcqWB0Df7w%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★ContextGen是一个创新的框架，利用用户提供的参考图像生成具有多个实例的图像，提供对其位置的布局控制，同时保证身份的一致性</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">。该项目提供了推理代码、训练代码、预训练模型权重以及图形用户界面（GUI）支持，旨在为用户提供便捷的多实例图像生成体验。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p><span style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/contextgen\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/contextgen</a></span></span></span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
